Resource Profile: CH ELM Observation Results for HIV Recency Testing (strict)

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-elm/StructureDefinition/ch-elm-observation-results-hiv-recency-strict Version: 1.13.0
Active as of 2025-11-25 Computable Name: ChElmObservationResultsLaboratoryHivRecencyStrict

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This CH ELM profile constrains the Observation resource for the purpose of laboratory test reports for hiv recency.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: CH ELM Composition: Laboratory Report

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
